      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Shoton Clan, Level 12+</p><p>Your Crystal release chakra is so solid, that it becomes the basis of your soul and fighting spirit. You gain the following Benefits;</p><p>• Increase your Constitution or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Ninjutsu you cast with the Earth Release keyword that creates an Earthen Construct that requires concentration no longer takes up a concentration slot.</p><p>• Shoton clan Hijutsu you cast that require concentration no longer require chakra to maintain concentration.</p>",
